    title: 'Commercial Construction Insurance: What Charlotte Business Owners Need to Know',
    slug: 'commercial-construction-insurance-charlotte',
    excerpt: 'Understanding commercial construction insurance protects your investment and your business. Here is everything Charlotte business owners need to know before breaking ground.',
